data.description: A True Gem in Flowery Branch.  A  Perfect Home for The Holidays. Welcome to this gorgeous and fully renovated home in a quiet, established, amenity  neighborhood in Cherokee Bluff school district. Move in ready! Perfect for the first home buyer. Open Concept.  The main floor features 3 Beautiful bedroom and 2 full baths. Hardfloors in the living area. Finished  Basement in which your buyer  will find a ideal suite for the in laws with a bedroom and a full bathroom.  New dishwasher and newer stove. New HVAC bought in August 2023. Large deck overlooks fenced in back yard. Neighborhood amenities includes Swimming pool and playground. A perfect house to be called Home.
